{"tid":130343,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[自hi]冇野做決定開個古典樂入門推薦post","createTime":"2017-02-22T10:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T22:19:26.000Z","uid":55511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7df08e0886c2c069f663caa8de4ef1a0feadc59","tid":130343,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"古典音樂真係好少人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開呢個post想話啲人得閒可以入黎望下<br />\n<br />\n對古典音樂有興趣但係唔知聽咩既自然可以跟住我比既link試下<br />\n有聽開既亦都可以試下自己冇聽過果啲<br />\n<br />\n鑑於古典音樂實在有太多流派同曲目 唔係話首首都岩自己心水 <br />\n加我自己亦不過係聽左五六年 未聽晒mahler bruckner 冇聽過wagner <br />\n深諳第一次聽個幾鐘頭(mahler果類)既苦悶 <br />\n因為有啲既複雜程度 並唔係一下啃得晒<br />\n而首歌岩唔岩聽亦可以睇番自己偏好<br />\n好似我自己唔係好鍾意法國類 <br />\n因此呢個post我主要係分享同探索<br />\n分享一兩個片段同樂章 帶新手認識下古典音樂同務求爽下聽耳 試下自己到底偏好邊類<br />\n我亦會post一啲比較冷門同艱深既曲目 好似<br />\nScriabin poem of ecstasy 這種需要一陣先消化到 同大家(小貓三四隻)探索下自己對古典音樂接受程度既邊界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4750982d492fe9b093c62e0d596b3230f38abd1d","tid":130343,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5921b219c6a2437c0c895891ee03b41e18a055","tid":130343,"uid":2423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"788ddd334ce1be45d81401b2624dae1d22485677","tid":130343,"uid":50080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"fef5825657009dfddcadd4424e03b89189189db2","tid":130343,"uid":2338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"fb5b5f49108a9b8378d305102f296324a7152bcc","tid":130343,"uid":52238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1c4da273f41025d475350f6bce3237b9ae6a2026","tid":130343,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1