"replyTime":"2017-03-18T18:05:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d244c058eb22d45ceb14486adf218d10f9b39771","tid":130343,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T20:55:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZWRp4UqyRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjZWRp4UqyRo&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ba524db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZWRp4UqyRo</a><br />\nhi<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我仲記得呢個POST 貼啲唔關事野先"},{"pid":"6e8f1a1060d8cd98aea917b38aa2a878524f79e3","tid":130343,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:19:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Aqj6u_7kFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Aqj6u_7kFM&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f7e13678\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Aqj6u_7kFM</a><br />\n有啲人問:咦喟我唔係好熟古典音樂 除左four season之外乜柒都唔識 咁應該點算好呀<br />\n我會答:除左坊間一啲&quot;古典101&quot; 或者上網搵入門LIST之外 跟住啲大師既推介都會係唔錯既選擇 大師講緊有三種 演奏家(soloist)<br />\n指揮家(conductor) 作曲家(composer)<br />\n我主要想講前兩類 soloist例如yoyo ma啦 大提琴黎講十分出名 一線 世界級 係youtube打佢個名你可以搵到好多大提琴既作品 而yoyo ma鍾意玩跨界 所以除左聽較舊既你仲可以聽到電影配樂同埋近代既 有趣既作品 例如佢既piazzolla<br />\n然後Itzhack perlman又係同佢差唔多鍾意咩都玩下又成日同yoyo ma合作既violinist啦 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yYikshdLcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0yYikshdLcw&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=069e75e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yYikshdLcw</a><br />\n<br />\nviolinist黎講我自己就鍾意比較後生上既vengerov<br />\n<br />\npianist出名既就有太多 但係唔同pianist就會有自己玩開果範(分時期,genre,主要跟作曲家) 因為曲目實在有太多啦<br />\n例如 Barenboim係beethoven,brahms, hamelin多rachmaninoff   rubinstein係chopin 內田光子mozart ,schubert<br />\npollini都好勁玩咩唔係好記得 我自己就鍾意kissin同yuja wang<br />\n<br />\n總結:好簡單 你覺得我呢到唔夠可以去wiki個演奏家列表<br />\n到撞下有冇岩心水既"}]}